s.text: And she, her back to him, seems only what she shows as she bends over, reaching between her splayed legsto pick it up, her face a moment upside down beneath her crotch, her pink tongue flickering levelwith the face she watches watching her, the face void

of themselves still outside watching what they onlyenter in the dark, what in the dark they only feel --Only imagine it, and it is yours, your eye, and mine,no less imperiously moving over him as his movesover the places in her she has never seen.
